<Assembly: AssemblyTitle("Savvy DOCX Recovery")> 
<Assembly: AssemblyDescription("Savvy DOCX Recovery is a simple GUI app which opens many corrupt MS Word files that Microsoft Word cannot.  The program works by categorizing Microsoft Word file opening errors and then fixing the documents with the most effective methods for recovery. For unpecified errors it removes the bad tags. For tags not matching errors it reorders the tag in the offending section. For all other errors it uses command line apps to try to repair the XML or salvage the text.")> 
